OL,5, Children in care are too often treated 
OL,6, in society as criminals rather than    
OL,7, victims, an independent body has said. 
OL,9,FApplications to build new care homes   
OL,10,Fare regularly met with hostility by    
OL,11,Fnearby residents, said the Independent 
OL,12,FChildren's Home Association (ICHA).    
OL,14,FChief executive Peter Sandiford urged  
OL,15,Fcommunities to view the wellbeing of   
OL,16,Fchildren above fears over house prices.
OL,18,FSince 2017 the number of children's    
OL,19,Fhomes in England has risen by at least 
OL,20,Fa quarter, to more than 2,700.         
